post.description:
Request body:
{
    "query": "show me LLM evals that are pass/fail",
    "schema": [
        {
            "field": "eval_type",
            "label": "Eval Type",
            "type": "enum",
            "operators": ["is", "is_not"],
            "choices": ["llm", "code", "agent"]
        },
        ...
    ]
}

Expected request data:
{
    "columns": [
        {
            "new_column_name": "column1",
            "column_type": "string",
            "source": "OTHERS"  # optional
        },
        {
            "new_column_name": "column2",
            "column_type": "number",
            "source": "OTHERS"  # optional
        }
    ]
}

Supports two modes:
1. JSON body: { name, columns, data, ... }
2. Multipart file upload: file (CSV/XLS/XLSX/JSON) + name field

Request body format:
{
    "eval_template_ids": ["uuid1", "uuid2", ...]
}

Request body:
{
    "sampling_rate": 0.2,  // Required: 0-1
    "status": "waiting"    // Optional: "waiting" or "paused"
}

Request body:
{
    "organization_id": "uuid",
    "platform_fee": 1500.00,
    "entitlements": {"monitors": -1, "has_knowledge_base": true, ...},
    "pricing": {
        "ai_credits": [
            {"tier_start": 0, "tier_end": 10000, "price_per_unit": 0.005},
            {"tier_start": 10000, "tier_end": null, "price_per_unit": 0.003}
        ], ...
    }
}
